
advocate/promote the culture to make data driven/informed decisions

(1) decision making cycle
prepare
decide
communicate
execute
measure and adjust


(2) how to make the call?
two dimensions: whether of the risk of being wrong is large, importance? how urgent to make decision?
autocratic: urgent not important
concensus: not urgent but important, big decision
participartory: urgent and important, gather some input then quickly make the call
democratic: not urgent, not important

